[21:26:33] J.D.: A career in medicine
can take you down
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:26:39] many different paths.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:26:40] Spreader!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:26:42] If you're lucky, you end up
