INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:26:45] Found it! Clamp!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:26:46] [ Flat line ]
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:26:48] Clamping.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:26:49] [ Monitor beeping ]
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:26:51] BP rising.
Great save, J.D.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:26:54] Great. Let's get him
to the O.R., guys.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
