INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:27:07] [ All chanting "Dorian!" ]
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:27:09] Nurse: Dr. Dorian?
Yeah.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:27:11] Will you sign my tattoo?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:27:12] Sure.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:27:13] That was a good hair day.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:27:15] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:27:16] Great job, man!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:27:18] Glad you're
feeling better.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:27:19] [ All chanting "Dorian!" ]
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:27:20] [ All cheering ]
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:27:23] ♪ I've had the time of my life ♪
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
INFO:     127.0.0.1:38964 - "GET /last HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:27:25] Frank: Dr. Dorian?
Dr. Dorian!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:27:29] [ Record scratches ]
Do I need stitches?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:27:31] Sure, being a concierge doctor
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:27:32] isn't nonstop excitement,
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:27:34] but I have more time
to see my kids...
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:27:35] No, Frank,
for cuts this small,
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:27:37] we just use
a little dab of glue.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:27:39] Fantastic job keeping
your food journal, Lisa.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:27:41] I just didn't expect
to see the word "smashburger"
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:27:43] on every page.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:27:45] It's really been
a full four hours?!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:27:47] We got to get that thing
down, Reggie.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:27:49] ...and making house calls
for the upper crust
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:27:50] sure pays well.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:27:52] I'm more concerned
with how it's leaning.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:27:54] Yep. This was my life now.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:27:55] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:27:57] That's why it felt so weird
to be back at Sacred Heart.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:28:00] I live an hour away,
but one of my patients
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
