[21:32:39] So, now that you're in town,
should we go out to dinner?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:32:42] Yes! Do you guys have
a place you usually go?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:32:44] Buddy, we haven't
been out to dinner
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:32:45] since the Disney princesses
were white.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:32:48] Besides, baby, I could
really use some man time.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:32:50] Turk was surrounded
by female energy.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:32:53] He had four daughters --
Izzie, Ellie, Sofia, and Nora.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:32:56] Love you. Izzie, Beetle,
take care of Ella-Bella.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:32:58] Daddy, why don't I
have a nickname?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:33:00] Oh, you do, sweetness.
You're "the accident."
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:33:04] Carla: Turk!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:33:05] Fine.
Have your guys' night out.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:33:07] Yes!
I'll see you later?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:33:08] See you later, guys.
Gimme some.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:33:10] Ow.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:33:11] Nostalgia washed over me.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:33:13] The smell
of the bleached floors,
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:33:15] the blinding
fluorescent lights,
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:33:18] the closet where Elliot and I
hid from our very first code.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:33:21] That's where
our love story began.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:33:23] Do me right here.
Okay.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:33:26] See?
Ugh!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:33:26] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:33:27] Ow!
Holy crap! J.D.!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:33:29] Good God!
You're like a blonde ninja!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:33:31] What the frick?
Why are you here?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:33:32] Oh, by the way,
our marriage didn't make it.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:33:34] I have a patient.
I'll be gone soon, I promise.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:33:36] Your promises mean
just about as much as...
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:33:38] ♪♪
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:33:42] Yes!
I'll see you later?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:33:43] Yes! Do you guys have
a place you usually go?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:33:44] So, now that you're in town,
should we go out to dinner?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:34:35] Yes! Do you guys have
a place you usually go?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:34:36] Buddy, we haven't
been out to dinner
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:34:38] since the Disney princesses
were white.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:34:40] Besides, baby, I could
really use some man time.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:34:42] Turk was surrounded
by female energy.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:34:45] He had four daughters --
Izzie, Ellie, Sofia, and Nora.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:34:48] Love you. Izzie, Beetle,
take care of Ella-Bella.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:34:51] Daddy, why don't I
have a nickname?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:34:53] Oh, you do, sweetness.
You're "the accident."
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:34:56] Carla: Turk!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:34:57] Fine.
Have your guys' night out.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:34:59] Yes!
I'll see you later?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:35:01] See you later, guys.
Gimme some.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:35:02] Ow.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:35:04] Nostalgia washed over me.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:35:25] The smell
of the bleached floors,
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:35:27] the blinding
fluorescent lights,
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
