[21:35:55] [ Both sigh ]
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:35:56] We agreed
in couples counseling
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:35:58] that in order to have
a healthy post-divorce life,
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:36:00] we need to respect
each other's space.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:36:01] I hate couples counseling.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:36:03] Could you please
be mindful of your tone
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:36:04] to avoid negative patterns
from our marriage?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:36:06] I love couples counseling!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:36:08] Look, J.D., I've really been
working on myself, okay?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:36:10] I have been lighting a candle
for every resentment
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:36:12] I had about our marriage
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:36:13] and floating them across
the pond at Winston Park.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:36:15] I'm in a good place!
I don't want to backslide!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:36:17] I can't just light
all those candles again!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:36:19] It was really cold, and I got
a ticket for scaring the ducks!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:36:22] [ Door opens, closes ]
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:36:24] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:36:25] There's my gal!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:36:26] Oh, goodness.
Johnathan.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:36:28] They've got teenagers
working here.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:36:30] Those are just interns,
Mrs. Brooks.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:36:32] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:36:33] Okay. Your labs look fine.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:36:35] I think
you're just dehydrated.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:36:37] Who admitted you?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:36:37] I did.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:36:39] Oh. Uh...
can I ask why?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:36:41] No judgment.
None taken.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:36:42] I admitted her
because I'm a good doctor.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:36:45] Oh.
Dr...Park, is it?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:36:47] When doctors fight
in front of a patient,
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:36:49] they always try
to make it sound friendly.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:36:51] These labs are normal
for a woman of her age.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:36:54] If it helps,
I could explain to you
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:36:57] what all these
fancy numbers mean.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:36:58] It's so nice to meet...
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:37:00] an incredibly
stupid person.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:37:03] Her abdominal pain
suggests ischemic bowel.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:37:05] No. All she needs is hydration
and emollient laxatives.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:37:07] [ Elevator bell dings ]
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:37:09] And there he was,
the Chief of Medicine,
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:37:11] my mentor.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:37:13] At least he couldn't
call me "Newbie" anymore.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:37:15] What can I do
for you, there, Oldie?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:37:17] Damn it.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:37:18] Perry, Dr. Park
here needs to know
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:37:20] that my medical expertise
is on par with his.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:37:22] Well, now, Dr. Park graduated
top of his class at Stanford,
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:37:25] whereas your current
claim to fame
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:37:27] is handing out erections like
tiny hot dogs at a bar mitzvah.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:37:31] Well, run a blood gas on her
and see who's right.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:37:33] [ Speaking Korean ]
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:37:34] Hmm!
[ Speaking Korean ]
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:37:37] Dr. Park is
teaching me Korean.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:37:39] Did I hear my name
in there?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:37:40] No. Walk with me.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:37:41] I, uh, heard
about the divorce.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:37:43] Sorry about that.
Also...
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:37:45] thankful I won $5
off of Mickhead.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:37:48] [ Speaking Korean ]
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:37:49] Damn it.
