[21:40:11] [ Chuckles ]
I took the under.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:40:13] Actually, it is good
to see you.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:40:16] I miss the days
when you were an intern.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:40:17] Aww. You don't
have to say that.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:40:19] I knew it! He's about to
ask you to play golf
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:40:20] at his fancy private club.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:40:22] Damn it! Why did you
only learn the mini kind?!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:40:23] Get a load
of this motley crew.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:40:26] [ Whimsical music plays ]
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:40:27] ♪♪
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:40:31] No. No, no. Sorry.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:40:32] I am not sure
how to teach these kids.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:40:35] I can't work them crazy hours
or even abuse them anymore.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "OPTIONS /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:41:56] And that's a bad thing?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:42:21] Exactly! I wasn't sure
if you'd get that.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:42:24] I am now
supposed to watch
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:42:26] every word that comes
out of my mouth
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:42:28] because apparently
they are all fragile
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:42:30] little Christmas
ornaments.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:42:31] Case in point.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:42:33] [ Whistles ]
TikTok doc!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:42:35] Oh. [ Chuckles ]
Hey, Dr. Cox.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:42:36] Tomorrow I am
going to perform
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:42:38] a central line placement,
and it would just be fabulous
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:42:41] if you could come in early
and observe.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:42:43] I'm good. I just
watched one on YouTube
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:42:45] like two days ago.
It slapped.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:42:47] Do you know Dr. Randy?
He's my favorite creator.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:42:50] He breaks down procedures
while doing bedtime ASMR.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:42:51] It'll give you
really graphic dreams.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:42:53] I'll send it to you.
You're gonna die.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:42:55] I will die
if you send it to me
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:42:57] 'cause then I'll just
have to murder you,
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:42:59] and with all these witnesses,
I think it's pretty safe
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:43:01] to assume they'll
give me the chair.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:43:04] Dr. Cox, I'm gonna need you
to go ahead and...
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:43:08] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:43:09] ...bring it down.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:43:10] Work-life balance
is a core principle
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:43:12] of our wellness program.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:43:14] Now, if you can't embrace that,
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:43:15] then you'll have to join me
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:43:17] at my sensitivity
training workshop.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:43:18] Don't I get
three strikes?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:43:20] You have 900 strikes.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:43:21] Mnh.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:43:22] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:43:24] That woman's like
the damn feelings police.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:43:26] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:43:27] Feelings police?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:43:29] Ugh!
Go change your shirt.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:43:32] You look chubby
in that.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:43:33] ♪ Feelings Police ♪
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:43:34] [ Tires screech, siren chirps ]
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:43:36] Whoa, whoa, whoa,
whoa, whoa!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:43:38] You know he's insecure
about his body.
Thank you!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:43:41] He's just not ready to show
you his vulnerability yet.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:43:43] Wow. You're really in touch
with male feelings.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:43:46] How do you think
I became a feelings cop?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:43:48] [ Moans ]
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:43:49] What the hell?!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:43:51] [ Horn honks,
car alarm blaring ]
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:43:52] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:43:53] I could help so many people.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:43:55] ♪♪
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:43:59] Hey.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:44:00] [ Dramatically ]
Good morning, sir.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:44:03] Dr. Chapstick
is flirting with you?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:44:05] I don't know.
I'm never sure.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:44:06] Last Thursday,
he did tell me
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:44:07] that he thought
I had a cute burp.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:44:09] Turk, thoughts?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:44:10] Yeah, he totally wants
to get on that flat ass.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:44:12] Score!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:44:14] I had planned to accidentally
burp near him again today,
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:44:16] but then J.D. threw me
off my game.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:44:17] Oh, stop worrying about J.D.
Here.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:44:19] [ Can opens ]
Chug half of that
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:44:21] and go launch a cute burp
into that man's face.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:44:23] Okay.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:44:25] [ Gulping ]
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:44:27] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:44:29] Hey, guys.
[ Burps ] Frick!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:44:30] I cannot believe
I wasted that on you!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:44:32] I actually miss those.
Ooh.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:44:34] Hey, by the way, if you
can get out of here early,
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:44:36] we can hit the happy hour that
has those awesome free wings.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:44:38] Dashana, can you go see
if there's an open O.R.?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:44:41] You know our diabetic guy,
Mr. Keefer?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:44:43] Let's move his toe
amputation up to now!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:44:44] On it, Dr. Turk!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:44:46] I'll tell the patient
it's a "free wing" issue.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:44:48] Don't do that.
Don't mention
the wings, please.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:44:49] Don't -- Don't do that.
No, no.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:44:50] Just one more test,
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:44:53] and if the results
are what I think they are,
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:44:55] I should be able to get you
out of here today, alright?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:44:56] Oh, thank goodness.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:44:58] Oldie, can you babysit these
for a minute, please?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:45:01] I need to go count to ten.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:45:03] This one asked
if he could shut his eyes
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:45:05] while I place
a central line.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:45:06] Admittedly, I do
still get a little woozy
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:45:08] around some procedures.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:45:10] All procedures.
All procedures.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:45:10] Mrs. Brooks: Ohh.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:45:12] Okay, well, let's start
by introducing yourself.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:45:14] This is Mrs. Brooks.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:45:15] I'm Dr. Green.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:45:17] I believe kindness
is the best medicine.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:45:18] Actually, medicine
is the best medicine.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:45:20] You're gonna get an arterial
blood gas on Mrs. Brooks.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:45:22] He's gonna do it?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:45:23] I'm gonna puke
if I do it.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:45:25] I don't want him
puking on me.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:45:25] If he pukes, I'll puke.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:45:27] No one is puking!
Okay? You got this.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:45:29] ♪♪
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:45:35] Mnh-mnh. Mnh-mnh!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:45:37] Oh, my God.
This is humiliating.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:45:40] Captain Bedside,
face that way.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:45:41] Yeah, I think that's
probably for the best.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:49:19] Now, don't be
overconfident.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:49:25] Finding the radial artery
can be tricky.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:49:26] I'm in.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:49:28] Nice job, Blake. You made
that look handsome -- easy.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:49:30] Easy does it.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:49:31] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:49:33] I got to admit,
I miss teaching.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:49:35] That's what this place
is all about.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:49:37] Dashana: Dr. Turk?
Hm?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:49:38] Maybe I could close?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:49:39] No. Just watch.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:49:41] Okay.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:49:43] Damn, I wish this guy
would just die all at once
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:49:44] instead of in
tiny little pieces.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:49:47] [ Monitor beeping ]
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:49:48] ♪♪
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:49:50] I don't know how much
more I can take of this,
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:49:52] but I'm not gonna let him
crush my spirit.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:49:53] We can't let
Dr. Bummer break us.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:49:56] See? This is what
I really miss! The hot goss!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:49:58] Who's Dr. Bummer?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:50:00] I don't know,
some other guy,
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:50:01] definitely not
your best friend.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:50:03] Turk's not a bummer.
He is the worst.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:50:05] There's no way,
and if he's ever in a bad mood,
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:50:07] all you gotta do is go,
"Wazzzzzzup,"
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:50:09] and he'll die laughing,
I swear. Try it.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:50:11] "Wazzup."
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:50:12] Go practice.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:50:14] Carla, do you know
Turk's interns
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:50:15] call him
"Dr. Bummer"?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:50:17] Well, I mean,
I'm sure you know
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:50:18] how dark Turk's been
at work lately.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:50:20] Just nod like you do.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:50:22] And he refuses
to talk about it.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:50:23] Y'all talking
about Dr. Turk?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:50:25] If so...prayers up.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:50:28] Even Hooch knows?!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:50:29] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:50:32] Is Hooch still crazy?
He's gotten worse.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:50:34] Doctor? There you go.
Thanks.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:50:36] Just what I wanted to see!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:50:37] [ Fingers snap ]
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:50:39] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:50:40] Hey, C-Bear, I was
right about my patient.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:50:42] Wanna come watch me rub it
in Dr. Cox's face
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:50:44] like the good old days?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:50:46] You know I do.
Hey, but you know what?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:50:47] You should chew
a big wad of gum.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:50:49] You always look tough
when you chew gum.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:50:51] I do look tough
when I chew gum.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:50:52] I hope they have
Berry Blast.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:50:54] ♪♪
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:50:56] Excuse me. Doctor?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:50:58] My wife's outside
in the car throwing up.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:51:01] It might just be
the stomach flu, but --
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:51:03] Sir, you're gonna
have to go through the E.R.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:51:04] I-If we go to the E.R.,
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:51:06] we're gonna be
crushed with bills.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:51:08] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:51:09] I think we'll just wait in
the car in case it gets worse.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:51:11] But could you just take
a quick look at her?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:51:14] Look, man.
[ Chuckles ]
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:51:16] You can't order healthcare
from your car, okay?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:51:19] It's a hospital,
not a Wendy's.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:51:20] Sorry.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:51:21] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:51:22] You didn't have to be
so harsh.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:51:24] If you want to go help him,
help him.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:51:25] You're gonna get fired,
but I think we'll all live.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:51:28] Let's go, Kim.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:51:29] Uh, it's Sam.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:51:30] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:51:31] [ Muffled ]
A word, Perry?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:51:32] Yeah, a word, Perry!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:51:34] [ Muffled ] So it turns out
Mrs. Brooks' blood ga--
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:51:36] I can't understand
a word you're saying.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:51:38] I know, 'cause this Hubba
has too much Bubba.
I can't control it.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:51:40] The Berry's blasting
all over my mouth!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:51:42] Give it to me.
Go ahead.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:51:43] Mrs. Brooks' blood gas
came back. She's not acidotic.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:51:46] Dr. Park, you were wrong.
Your boy botched it.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:51:49] While my boy here
needs the burn unit
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:51:50] because he's on fire.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:51:52] You both owe me
an apology.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:51:53] I'd rather
self-circumcise.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:51:55] Ah.
Gum me.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "OPTIONS /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:51:57] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:51:58] You two idiots are perfect
for each other.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:52:00] He's not wrong,
by the way.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:52:01] Our marriage
would have lasted.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:52:03] Yeah, it would have.
Let's get wings.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:52:05] You look so tough
right now.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:52:08] That went so well
with Dr. Cox,
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:52:09] I decided to press my luck.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:52:11] What's been going on
with you, man?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:52:12] I'm hearing
you're in a rough place.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:52:14] Nah.
That's nothing.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:52:14] Your interns call you
"Dr. Bummer."
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:52:16] You know, I really don't want
to talk about it right now.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:52:18] I just want to go out
and blow off some steam.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:52:21] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:52:22] Actually, Turk,
just hold on one second.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:52:23] Oh, boy.
Come on, man.
What is up?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:52:26] I'm burnt out!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:52:29] Okay? My patient today
is a perfect example.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:52:31] Once he heals,
he's gonna ignore my advice
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:52:34] and go right back to drinking
and eating garbage.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:52:36] I'll keep
removing body parts
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:52:38] until he eventually
dies on my table.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:52:40] And his family will ask me,
"Why couldn't you do more?"
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:52:43] You know, back in the day
when you were here,
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:52:44] we could at least
get up on the roof and...
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:52:46] we could laugh the day off
with a couple of beers.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:52:48] But we can't...
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:52:50] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:52:52] We can't do that anymore,
can we?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:52:54] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:52:56] There's no joy. None.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:52:58] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:52:59] Why haven't you
told me this?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:53:00] I could have
been there for you.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:53:02] I don't think
you can relate
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:53:03] to what I'm going through
anyway. I mean...
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:53:05] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:53:07] You write scripts
in the suburbs.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:53:08] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:53:10] I don't feel like going out
anymore. I'm gonna go home.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:53:13] Turk!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:53:13] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:53:15] Wazzzzzzup!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:53:17] Not tonight, J.D.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:53:19] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:53:20] Ooh! You okay?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:53:21] No.
Good.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:55:16] Did you at least
discharge my patient?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:55:37] Dr. Cox wants me
to keep her for another night.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:55:40] Toodles.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:55:41] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:55:42] Are you kidding me?!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:55:43] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:55:46] I was doing my best angry walk
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:55:48] because after Turk told me
he was going home last night,
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:55:51] I heard he went out
with someone else.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:55:53] What the hell, man?!
You went out with The Todd?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:55:55] I knew with you
it'd be therapy.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:55:56] I didn't want
to go deep.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:55:57] The Todd
really likes to go deep!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:56:00] With consent five.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:56:02] [ Smack! ]
[ Fingers snap ]
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:56:03] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:56:04] Hey, Carla, if you were
planning on having sex
with Turk tonight, don't!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:56:07] He doesn't deserve it!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:56:09] She's not!
Their sex night's Thursday!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:56:11] Stop telling
everyone what to do!
Elliot!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:56:13] What? I didn't even mention
that you do it in the
minivan 'cause of the kids.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:56:16] [ Groans ]
I'm sorry.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:56:17] I've just been
a little bit tense
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:56:19] because someone decided
to keep J.D.'s patient
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:56:21] here a little bit longer.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:56:22] Why is J.D. being here
so very hard on you?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:56:24] Aren't you the one
who ended the marriage?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:56:26] Where did you hear that?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:56:28] Who can say?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:56:29] Carla!
Barbie...
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:56:31] Carla and I have been
sharing secrets since before
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:56:33] you and your sorority sisters
were in Panama City
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:56:36] flashing the cameras
for "Girls Gone Wild."
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:56:38] I was told they
would be pixelated!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:56:40] Elliot is in a lot
of pain, okay?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:56:42] Okay?
Ah, yes.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:56:43] In the history
of relationships,
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:56:45] it has always been hardest
on the one who ends it.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:56:47] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:56:50] I'm not being a jerk,
am I?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:56:51] Oh. Sweetie.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:56:53] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:56:55] It's gonna be fine.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:56:56] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:56:58] ♪♪
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:57:00] The second I saw Dr. Cox,
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:57:02] I turned my angry walk
right back on.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:57:05] Why is Mrs. Brooks
still here?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:57:07] Why do you have the physique
of a menopausal lesbian?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:57:08] Whoa! Too mean!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:57:10] Not now, Oldie.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:57:11] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:57:12] This is frustrating.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:57:14] You gave me
the impression
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:57:16] that you were able
to place a central line
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:57:18] since you learned
from your...
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:57:20] Dr. Randy, was it?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:57:22] Yeah, but he was
really chill,
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:57:24] and you're giving
"mean football coach" vibes.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:57:26] Miss Tosh...
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:57:28] And you'll notice I'm not
saying "Dr. Tosh"...
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:57:29] Sibby: Dr. Cox?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:57:31] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:57:33] Ohh!
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:57:34] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:57:35] Thank you.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:57:36] You know...
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:57:38] it used to be
"see one, do one, teach one."
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:57:42] Alas, now it is "see one,
see one, see one, see one,
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:57:45] see one more,
call your therapist,
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:57:47] talk about
how it felt to see one,
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:57:49] decide that seeing one
is just too triggering,
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:57:52] take a Xanax to calm down
and Adderall to lock in,
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:57:56] and...finally focus enough
to be able to write
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:57:58] about the whole ordeal
in your dream journal."
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:58:01] Of course, if your dream
is to be a mediocre doctor,
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:58:04] mission accomplished.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:58:05] And, by all means,
hang on to the scrubs.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:58:07] Maybe use them for Halloween,
'cause you're damn sure
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:58:11] not gonna be using them
around here much longer.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:58:13] Okay.
I'll see you Saturday.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:58:15] Worth it.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:58:16] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:58:17] ♪ Feelings Police ♪
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:58:19] What?
Oh, it's this little song
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:58:20] I hear in my head
whenever I see you.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:58:22] Oh. I love it.
♪ Feelings Police ♪
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:58:25] You got it.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:58:26] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:58:27] Hey. You can do this.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:58:30] Guide that finder needle
into the jugular.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:58:31] She's gonna
nick that artery.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:58:33] No, she's not.
She's not nicking anything.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:58:34] You got this, Sam.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:58:35] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:58:39] Is it on my face?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:58:41] No.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:58:42] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:58:43] No, no, no.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:58:44] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:58:45] Why don't you
go take a couple, okay?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:58:47] 5, 10, 15.
Whatever you need.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:58:49] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:58:51] Keep going.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:58:52] And she did it.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:58:54] [ Excited chatter ]
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:58:56] And only one person
wasn't psyched for her.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:58:58] Hey, Blake?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:59:00] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:59:01] Just a little advice.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:59:02] You can't keep alienating
everyone, okay?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:59:05] This job is really rough.
You're gonna need people.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:59:07] Well, I'm not a kid like them,
so don't worry about me.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:59:10] I'll be fine.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:59:11] Not if nobody
has your back.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:59:13] Trust me.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:59:14] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:59:15] Gotta go.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:59:16] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:59:20] That's why I kept
your patient here.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:59:22] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:59:23] I'm sorry. What?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:59:24] To keep you here.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:59:26] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:59:28] You needed a reminder
of how very good you are
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:59:30] at what you do.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:59:31] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:59:32] Getting her
through that procedure,
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:59:34] that inspiring nonsense
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:59:35] you just said to that
gorgeous young man.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:59:38] I can't do that.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:59:39] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:59:41] I want you to come back.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:59:42] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:59:43] Are you
messing with me?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:59:45] No.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:59:46] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:59:47] Come back.
Make a difference.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:59:49] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:59:51] At least give it
some thought.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:59:52] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:59:55] Dr. Dorian.
Can I talk to you?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[21:59:58] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:00:01] I'm about to go into
surgery. What the hell
are you guys doing?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:00:04] All right, Dashana,
tell him what you told me.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:00:05] Well, Dr. Turk,
uh, the reason
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:00:08] I chose this hospital was
because of you, okay?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:00:10] All I kept hearing was
how great Dr. Turk is.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:00:14] You're, like, the only
other Black surgeon
in this place, okay?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:00:16] The rest of them just got, like,
Coldplay on loop in the O.R.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:00:21] and say stuff like,
"Wow. You're so articulate."
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:00:23] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:00:25] I guess I just thought
you'd be my guy.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:00:27] J.D.: Great job.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:00:29] Now we leave so he can
feel horrible about himself.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:00:31] No, Dashana, you stay.
You're gonna close.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:00:34] Are you good with that?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:00:35] Yeah, sure.
Yeah. No problem.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:00:38] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:00:44] Turk:
Oh, and, Dashana?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:00:46] This brother
likes Coldplay, too.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:00:49] [ Coldplay's "Clocks" plays ]
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:00:51] ♪♪
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:01:00] I had no idea what to do
about Dr. Cox's job offer,
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:01:03] so I decided to sleep on it.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:01:05] Sometimes when
you feel a little lost,
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:01:07] the world gives you a sign.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:01:08] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:01:10] It's just not always
a good one.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:01:11] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:01:12] What's the status?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:01:14] She was found
unresponsive in her car.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:01:15] Heart attack. We're trying.
But she's gone.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:01:18] ♪ You ♪
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:01:24] Why couldn't you
have helped us?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "OPTIONS /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:03:29] ♪ Are ♪
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:03:31] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:03:33] I had seen these moments
too many times.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:03:36] He just said it was
a stomachache. I...
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:03:39] You can't get through them
on your own.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:03:41] ♪♪
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:03:46] This wasn't your fault.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:03:47] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:03:49] Could have happened
to any one of us.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:03:50] It would have taken me
one minute
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:03:52] to just walk out there
and check on her.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:03:53] Now she's dead 'cause
I didn't walk outside.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:03:56] I should have
done something.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:03:58] ♪♪
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:04:00] ♪ Home, home,
where I wanted to go ♪
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:04:05] And like that,
I knew what my decision was.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:04:08] Hey.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:04:09] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:04:10] What are you
still doing here?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:04:11] I thought you'd be
long gone by now.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:04:13] I'll take the job.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:04:15] Oh, I'm quite glad.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:04:17] Perry, working
alongside you
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:04:19] will be one of the great
honors of my life.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:04:20] I should have been clear.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:04:22] You're not going to
be working with me.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:04:24] You're going to be me.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:04:26] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:04:28] You're the new
Chief of Medicine.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:04:30] What?
[ Chuckling ] No.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:04:33] I can't be you.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:04:34] You're right.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:04:36] Just be you.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:04:38] This particular world
has passed me by.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:04:42] You're the only one I trust
to do better and try harder.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:04:45] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:04:46] Perry, I really
don't think I --
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:04:48] J.D., those interns
need somebody
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:04:51] to do for them
what I did for you.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:04:53] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:04:54] Okay?
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:04:55] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:04:57] Dr. Park
really wanted this job.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:05:00] And his hatred for you
is going to burn quite hot.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:05:03] And that thought...
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:05:05] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:05:07] ...will keep me warm
at night.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:05:10] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:05:13] I have never been a boss.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:05:15] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:05:16] I've never even run
a lemonade stand.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:05:18] But one thing's for sure.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:05:20] I can't do this all on my own.
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
[22:05:23] @keyframes caption-blinker { 50% { opacity: 0.0; } }
INFO:     100.81.62.97:0 - "POST /subtitle HTTP/1.1" 200 OK
